title: Montagnes en Tete PDTV x265-MVGroup
description:
Mountain Dreams.

Four mountaineers, Dani Arnold, Stephan Siegrist, Werner Munter and Jacques Grandjean come up against questions that we all ask ourselves at some point: what price am I willing to pay to live my dream? Do I need to take this risk in life? Directed by Matthias Affolter.
